title: Watch: Chattanooga's Greg Pryor makes ridiculous shot while falling out of bounds

Watch: Chattanooga's Greg Pryor makes ridiculous shot while falling out of bounds Eric Vander Voort | NCAA.com Contact | Archive | RSS 
You don't see a shot like this every day. 
In the second half of Thursday night's win against UNCG, Chattanooga senior guard Greg Pryor poked the ball loose in the backcourt, chased it down, and chucked up a shot as he was falling out of bounds. It went in. â€” Chattanooga Mocs MBB (@GoMocsMBB) February 3, 2017
